SC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 word"> time, He expects that His Servants <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="3 letters">ligently attend the work He calls <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 word"> to; and that they should not <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 word"> themselves in Sleep and Sloth. <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 word">
