<P N="2">2. If He should do so, there is da<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="2 letters">ger lest they be found Sleeping&punc; whic<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter"> would be very uncomfortable, sin<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="2 letters"> the Lord had Commanded them <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 word"> Watch. For a Watch-man to <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 word"> found Sleeping is a sad thing. <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 word"> Christians are appointed Watch-men therefore should be careful that th<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter"> Lord may not find them Sleeping at <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 word"> Coming. There is a <HI>Three-fold</HI> Coming <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 word"> Christ intended here. There is His P<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="3 letters">vidential Coming, to take Vengeanc<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter"> on the <HI>Iewish</HI> Nation. And there is <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 word"> Personal Coming to Judge the World&punc; And His Coming at the Hour of Deat<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">&punc; At present our Discourse will be <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 word"> with respect to that Coming&punc;</P>
<DIV2 TYPE="doctrine">
