<P N="4">4. <HI>They that are not only Strangers but Sojourners, do not abide long where they are.</HI> And thus it is with the Ser|vants of God&punc; they abide not long where they are: They are Sojourners, they are Travelling, there is <HI>none <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 word"> <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">iding</HI> for them here: Mic. 2.18. <HI><GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 word">
